About me


Xuan Yang holds PhD from Department of Information Systems, City University of Hong Kong. She is currently working in the Southern University of Science and Technology. Her research interests include open innovation, business analytics, social media and social network, HCI, knowledge management, economics of information systems, Fintech et.al. She has published papers in International Journal of Information Management and several top and main IS conferences including International Conference on Information Systems, Hawaii International Conference on System Sciences, Pacific Asia Conference on Information Systems and Americas Conference on Information Systems. 
